      _TV Show Notes_ 
      ===============----------------------------------------------------
                                   
       To celebrate the forthcoming release of the heavy metal group's
       first album for five years, Death Magnetic, Verity Sharp visits 
       Norway to gain access to their summer tour of Europe. Going 
       backstage, she captures their rehearsals and pre-show activities
       and interviews band stalwarts James Hetfield and Lars Ulrich

